## Commands

```bash
[%- if .HasCLI %]
make build          # Build binary → ./bin/[% .BinaryName %]
[%- end %]
make test           # Run tests
make lint           # Run linters (golangci-lint)
make format         # Format code (gofumpt)
```

## Architecture

```
[%- if .HasCLI %]
cmd/[% .BinaryName %]/      # CLI entry point (cobra)
  main.go             # Binary entry point
  root.go             # Root command + flag setup
  version.go          # Version subcommand
  ui.go               # Terminal output helpers
  help.go             # Custom help formatting
internal/
  version/            # Version info injected via ldflags
[%- end %]
[%- if .HasLib %]
pkg/[% .LibPackage %]/      # Public library package
  testdata/           # Test fixtures
[%- end %]
assets/               # Demo content (GIFs, screenshots)
[%- if .CIGitHub %]
.github/workflows/    # GitHub Actions CI[% if .Goreleaser %] + release[% end %]
[%- end %]
[%- if .CIGitLab %]
.gitlab-ci.yml        # GitLab CI[% if .Goreleaser %] + release[% end %]
[%- end %]
```

