## Coding Standards

- Functions under 40 lines
- Errors wrapped with context: `fmt.Errorf("doing X: %w", err)`
- Map-based table tests: `map[string]struct{}`
- Accept interfaces, return concrete types

## File Conventions

- Templates use `[% "[%" %] [% "%]" %]` delimiters (avoids conflicts with goreleaser `{{ }}`)
- Shell scripts in `scripts/` are `chmod +x`
[%- if .HasLib %]
- Test fixtures in `pkg/[% .LibPackage %]/testdata/`
[%- end %]
- Environment variable prefix: `[% .EnvPrefix %]`
